{"tid":1042020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"目擊者: 74歲老婦匆忙走出馬路被旅遊巴撞","createTime":"2019-03-01T09:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T09:22:41.000Z","uid":42188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6806920a044432947f5f9f2c29dada0e49e29427","tid":1042020,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:07:04.000Z","msg":"油麻地甘肅街玉器市場對開，早上10時48分發生交通意外。一名婦人被一輛旅遊巴撞倒，頭部重創，鮮血直流。附近油麻地分科診所的醫護人員得悉車禍，最少5人跑出來協助，替傷者急救，稍後再交由救護車將傷者送院。<br />\n<br />\n傷者姓陳74歲，送廣華醫院搶救，目前情況危殆。警方封鎖現場調查，並翻看附近店舖的閉路電視錄影。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一位目擊者指，見到傷者匆忙走出馬路，「嘭」一聲被旅遊巴撞倒，「架車（旅遊巴）開得好慢好慢㗎喇！」</span><br />\n<br />\n又一個賽跑冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad707a41380a6b020ed9a3fc314ad6888a4b6e9","tid":1042020,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"生前係賽跑冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b4d79d685c7241e016951bedf991eaeb8acf21","tid":1042020,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"恭喜哂呀婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3077397489d8b9d6c38c3dc70010a0327451b74b","tid":1042020,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bad707a41380a6b020ed9a3fc314ad6888a4b6e9","tid":1042020,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"生前係賽跑冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"人哋未死危殆喳，不過都快㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d97adca8a4f4f734a7fdfb50b2f40e2b7c36178","tid":1042020,"uid":100766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"真係好多老野自動申請早啲落去<br />\n你想落去唔緊